Title: Eating Out: The Open Weekend
Writer: Phillip J. Bartell, Q. Allan Brocka
Actors: Aaron Milo, Chris Puckett, Chris Salvatore, Harmony Santana
Plot: Zack is gaycationing in Palm Springs with new BF Benji who, to Zack's dismay, wants to try an open relationship. Adding confusion is Casey, Zack's ex, with Peter, his fake BF, plus Casey's fruity friend, Penny, and Zack's friend Lilly.
